sentences.english: A willow warbler is similar to the greater whitethroat but smaller.
sentences.chinese: 柳鶯與大白喉鶯相似，但體型較小。

sentences.english: Looks like a worn and moulting Arctic Warbler.

sentences.english: I am interested with this warbler!

sentences.english: On blazing Monday I heard the year's first chiffchaff.
